column2: Migrated from EPA STORET Legacy Database- originally reported by Wisconsin DNR
Tree pollen in + on water.  Lake level: very high
Odor on + around lake continues.  Has been noticed since 6/1/94.
Heavy rain recently.  Lake up by April 10'.
No clarity and odor problems this year (as opposed to last year) despite high water temperatures.
Last reading of the year.  Have a good winter!
Light winds- hazy sunshine- lots of tree pollen in the water.
Light winds- lots of tree pollen in the water.  Some rain yesterday.
Light winds.  Approximately one inch of rain yesterday.
Light winds.  Heavy boat traffic through 7/7 due to holiday.  Some algae blooms in shallow areas also.
Partly sunny- 15 mph wind- heavy storms 46 hours ago.
Mostly sunny- light wind- heavy rain 2 days ago.
Sunny- light wind- lake "turn over" recently.
Sunny with light wind- very windy yesterday- 20 mph gusts.
First check of the year.  Light wind.  Ice off approximately 10 days ago.  Water is up about 10 inches since last fall.  Lake level: very high
Light wind.  Lake level: very high
Light wind.  Lake level: very high
Mild wind.  Some tree pollen on the water.  Very little rain this spring.  Lake level: very high
Very light wind- and sunny.  Some rain yesterday.  Also some pollen in the water.  Lake level: very high
Sunny and mild wind.  Heavy rain two days ago.  Lake level: very high
Clear skies- some debris in shallow water near shore from run-off.
Mostly sunny.  10-15 mph wind.  Lake level: very high
Sunny- mild wind.  Lake level: very high
Weather calm and warm.  Lake level: very high
Sunny- mild wind.  Some heavy rain yesterday.  Lake level: very high
Mostly sunny- light wind.  Noticed some algae bloom in the shallows.  Lake level: very high
Partly cloudy- mild wind.  Some algae bloom.  Lake level: VERY HIGH BUT HAS GONE DOWN.
Mostly sunny with light wind. about an inch of rain yesterday.  Lake level: VERY HIGH BUT HAS GONE DOWN.
Partly sunny and calm.  About 1/2 inch of rain early this morning.  Little boat traffic since Labor Day.
A perfect day.  Crystal clear and 70 degrees.
Sunny and calm.  Had a little more than an inch of rain three days ago.
Hazy sunshine light wind.  Ice out 3 weeks ago.  Few lily pads in shallows.
Mostly sunny- mild wind. Some tree pollen on water.
Sunny light wind.  Lots of tree pollen on water.
Sunny mild wind. strong wind last night.  Tree pollen on water.
Partly sunny light wind. 10 degree water temp.  Drop in last week.
Mostly sunny light wind.  2+" rain and hail 4 days ago.
Partly sunny mild wind.  Some rain recently.
Sunny light wind.  Had a good rain shower yesterday.
Sunny light wind.  No rain in several weeks.  Algae blooms in shallows.
Hazy sunshine light wind.  Still no rain.
Clear light wind. 80 degrees beautiful day.
1st check of year. Sunny + 60 F. Calm to light wind. Beautiful spring day- eagles soaring- loons singing. Ice out about 2 weeks ago.
Light wind- lots of tree pollen on water.  About 4 inches of rain several days ago.
Light wind. Some pollen on water.
Mostly sunny- light wind.  Some heavy rain showers yesterday.
Partly sunny- light wind.  Some showers in recent days.
Partly sunny- hot + humid- light wind.
Mostly sunny- mild wind.  Some algae blooms in shallows.
Very heavy boat traffic last weekend.
Clear skies. Calm to light wind. What a beautiful day!
Beautiful sunny 60 F fall day. Light wind.
Clear sky.  Light wind.  Nice day.  Last check of year.  Happy Holidays.
Finally the weather cooperates when I am there- first check of year- nice sunny day- light wind.
Partly sunny with a light wind.
Sunny- calm wind- some good showers yesterday afternoon- a little pollen on water.
Mostly cloudy- mild wind- some tree pollen on water.
Mostly cloudy- lots of rain lately- water is up approximately 1.5" from one week ago.
Cloudy- but calm- lots of debris on water surface from a lot of boats (4th of July).
Partly sunny- light wind- heavy rain several days ago- some algae in shallows.
Mostly sunny- light wind- some algae blooms in shallows- water is up about 2.5" since mid June.
Sunny- calm- no significant rain in 11 days- algae bloom in shallows.
Sunny- light winds- some light showers last few days.
Sunny- calm wind- some heavy rain a few days ago- algae blooms in shallows getting bigger.
Sunny with clouds moving in- light winds getting stronger- algae not as noticeable.
Sunny- light winds getting stronger- algae noticeable in shallows.
Clouding up- rain coming tonight- strong winds- clear in shallows.
Sunny- light wind- beautiful fall day.
Nice day- sunny with a light wind. Lots of pollen in the water.
Sunny- in fact the most sun since last check- calm wind- and still some pollen but not as noticeable.
Light winds. Few clouds- hazy. Lots of stuff floating in water. Heavy rain last night.
Sunny- light wind- and couldn't do test on the 21st when the satellite was here cause of the rain.
Sunny- mild wind- and hot with the temperature at 80 degrees.
Sunny- light winds- cool this morning but beautiful now- and saw four loons.
Cold all week- the temperature is 80 degrees today- light winds- few hazy clouds- and satellite today.
Mostly cloudy- just a few peeks of the sun. Calm wind. Algae blooms evident in shallows.
Mostly sunny- light wind- some good rain yesterday- and algae blooms in shallows.
Very hot- sunny and calm wind- good day to lay in the lake.
Sunny- the temperature is around 90 degrees- strong wind at 10-15 mph- and test to match the satellite study.
Sunny- light winds- temperature at 72 degrees- test to match the satellite today.
Partly sunny. Light wind. Not too many boaters on lake.
Skies are clear- 10 mph winds- the temperature is 78 degrees- and rained all day on Saturday.
Partly cloudy- temp in the 70's. 10-20 mph wind.
Skies are clear- over 10 mph winds- the temperature is 70 degrees- and secchi test to match the satellite.
Mostly sunny- light wind- beautiful first day of fall- trees are changing and the fish are biting.
Sunny- light wind- warm out- and tree color is about peak.
Cold- windy- and snow flakes coming down. White caps on lake.
Last check of the year.  Nice day too- blue skies- light wind- and upper 40s.
Mostly sunny with light wind- first check of year and 1st day of vacation.
Cloudy- windy- and clod. Randy and I did test together.
Cloudy- 5-10 mph winds. Rained all Saturday. Rained today coming in from test
Hazy sunshine- light wind. Some tree pollen on water
Sunny and light wind- pollen on water. Cold and rainy last couple of days
Cloudy- light wind. Pollen on water in shallows. A lot of rain last night
Sunny- 10-15 mph winds. Light rain last night- .2"
Partly sunny- light wind- one inch of rain overnight. We've got a rain gauge now
Sunny- light winds. 70 deg F. Do test before all boats start going
Sunny with a light wind. Beautiful day
Sunny- 74 F. 10 mph winds. Real muggy- storms coming tonight!
Sunny- light wind. Cool temp- beautiful day. Algae blooms in shallows
Cloudy- light wind. 82 F air temp
Sunny- 76 F. Windy 15 mph or so. Got secchi to compare with satellite.
Sunny- mild wind. Almost 3 inches of rain in last 1 1/2 weeks
Another beautiful day. Sunny with light wind. Temps in the 70's
Sunny- 74 F- 5-10 mph winds. Got secchi before it rains this weekend
Clear blue sky- calm wind. Warm- supposed to be 80's. Last nice day of summer
Sunny- light wind- nice fall day
Sunny- 10 mph wind. Cold- in the low 40's. Water is warmer than the air
Partly sunny. 10 mph winds. Crisp day- had a snow shower this morning
First secchi check of season.  Mostly cloudy- light wind.
Nice day- sunny and 10 mph wind. Good water clarity considering 2.1 inches of rain on Mother's Day.
Beautiful holiday weekend. Warm and sunny. Light wind. Lots of pollen on water and boat traffic.
Nice day- light winds. 55 F air temp. Got 1 in rain Friday. Pollen on water- but water clear.
Nice day- light winds. Got 1 1/10 in of rain yesterday. Temp 62 F. Did secchi to match satellite.
Mostly sunny- bit cool and a tad windy.
Hazy sunshine- light wind and warm too. 75 F. Little pollen on water also.
Warm day- temp 77 F. 10 mph winds. Was diving the day of the satellite. Got Secchi today.
Sunny- warm- light wind. Couldn't ask for a better holiday weekend.  Lots of boats too!
Nice holiday weekend. Temp 72 F. Light winds. Lot of big boats on lake- did secchi to match satellite.
Sunny and light wind- some algae blooms in shallows.
Partly sunny and light wind. First water sampling and temp readings with new equipment. Thanks Sandy!
Sunny and a mild wind. Algae blooms in shallows. Not much rain in the last month.
Beautiful day- sunny and a light wind.
Rain on and off the last 4 days. Temp 68 F. Wind 5-15 mph. Did secchi to match satellite.
Partly sunny and a tad cool - nice day.
Light winds- temp 80 F. Did secchi to match satellite today.
Temp 84 F. Windy. Got 8/10 in rain last night. Did Secchi to match satellite yesterday.
Cool day. Temp 64 F. Light winds. Did Secchi to match satellite today.
Temp 43 F- light winds- got rain this week and snow up by Eagle River.
Clear- blue sky. No wind- 70 F. What a beautiful day- and besides all that- what a Secchi Depth!
Hazy blue sky- light wind. Warm too - 60s- with peak color in the trees!
Sunny- light wind- cool.  In the 40s.  Ice out approximately 16 days ago.
Sunny- light wind.  Some pollen on water.
Sunny- light winds- temp. 55 F.  Pollen on the water.  2/10 in. rain the other day.
Clear blue sky- light wind- beautiful day!
Partly sunny- light wind.  Over 2 inches of rain within last week.
Temp. 65 F.  Winds about 10 mph.  Got 3/10 in. rain yesterday.
Mostly sunny- light wind.  Water has a cloudy look to it.
Hazy sunshine- light wind- not too warm- a perfect summer day.
Sunny- calm to light wind.  Algae blooms in shallows.
Clear today.  Got 1 1/2 inches of rain in last 2 days.  Temp. 60 F.
Temp. 64 F- sunny- got 1.5 inches of rain this week.
Sunny after a foggy morning.  Light wind.  Algae blooms in shallows.
Sunny- temp. 72 F.  10 mph winds.  Algae still in shallow water.
Sunny- temp. 76 F.  Lite winds.  Little algae in shallow water.
Clear blue sky- light wind.  Cool temperatures.  A beautiful fall day.
Clear skies- another nice fall day.  A bit windy. 10-15 mph.
Sunny- windy and cool.  None the less- a beautiful fall day.
First check of year from row boat.  Mostly sunny.  Light wind.  Little rain yesterday.
Partly sunny- calm wind- cool spring day.  Some pollen on water.  Awesome clarity.
Sunny- light wind.  Rain showers totaling .3 of an inch over last several days.  Some pollen on water.
Got over an inch of rain in the last 4 days.  Cloudy and windy today.
Mostly sunny- sort of windy in test area.  Over 2 inches of rain in last eight days.
Did Secchi to match satellite today.  Windy.  10-15 mph winds.  Got over 2 inches of rain last week.
Sunny- warm and a bit breezy.
Sunny- warm- temp. 70 F.  Light winds.
Sunny- 72 F.  Over 1/2 inch of rain last 2 days.  Lots of boats tearing up shore vegetation.
Warm and sunny with a mild wind.  Some algae blooms in shallows.
Mostly sunny- light wind- hot- hot and did I say it's hot out - low 90s.
Partly cloudy- light wind- algae in shallows.
Warm- hazy sunshine with about a 15 mph wind.  About 2 1/3 inches of rain last week.
Light breeze- temp. 72 F.  Algae blooms in shallows.
Partly sunny- breezy - 15 mph wind- cool 59 F temp.  An inch of rain last week.
Cloudy- temp. 76 F.  Got 1/2 inch of rain this week and the lake is still going down.
Hazy sunshine- a little breezy.  Beautiful holiday weekend.
Temp. 72 F- breezy.  Did Secchi to match up with satellite.
Hazy- warm- humid and a light wind.
Sunny- warm and a light wind.  A beautiful late summer day.
Sunny with a light wind- cool but seasonal.  Approximately 2 1/2 inches of rain in the last week.
Sunny with a mild wind.  Warm in the mid 70s.  Beautiful fall colors too.
Sunny- light wind.  Almost 2 inches of rain last week.

Sunny- calm wind.  A beautiful day with lots of leaves on the ground.  Additional comments:  Lake level has gone down approximately one foot due to the hot dry summer.  Also the algae blooms weren't as prevalent- possibly because there wasn't much submerged shoreline vegetation.
partly cloudy- light wind- nice spring day
Sunny- light wind- a cool morning.  About 3 inches over the past few weeks.  Lots of tree pollen on water too.
Sunny- mild wind- and hot.  80s.  Little over 1 inch of rain 2 days ago and 2.5" for the week.
Not a cloud in the sky- with a lite breeze.  Beautiful day!
Mostly sunny- light wind- a tad cool- but nice- about 3/4 inch of rain last week
Nice day- sunny- lite wind.  Not too hot- not too cool.
A light shower this morning- but mostly sunny and a lite wind now.
Mostly sunny and a lite wind.
Hot- sunny and windy- only .1 inch of rain yesterday morning very little for the last month- some algae blooms in shallows
At last- .3 inches of rain early this morning and more coming later.  Sunny and a little breezy now.
Approximately 4 inches of rain in the last week- wow.  Sunny- hot- humid with a breeze.  Algae in shallows.
Sunny- calm day- 72 F temp.  No rain all week.
Sunny- lite breeze.  Temp 73 F.  Some algae in shallows.
Sunny with a lite wind- a nice and comfortable day
Clear blue sky with a calm wind.
Temp. 70 F.  Lite winds.  Gonna get rain this weekend.
Clear blue sky- lite wind- a beautiful fall day- about one inch of rain in the last week
Clear sky with a mild wind.  Very windy several days and about 3 inches of snow in past week.
Last check of the year.  Sunny and a bit breezy- but a nice fall day.
Warm - upper 70s.  Clear skies- but rather breezy.
Hazy sunshine with a 10-15 mph wind.
Light wind- clear skies.  Nice and warm too!
Beautiful summer day with a clear sky and light wind.
Sunny with a light wind.  3/4 inch of rain several days ago.  Some algae in shallows.
Sunny and windy.  Some algae clouds in shallows.
Sunny.  FInally- temps in the 70s.  Wind about 10-15 mph.
Mostly sunny and breezy.  Nice holiday weekend.
Warm and breezy fall day.  Beautiful tree color too.
Sunny and calm wind in test area.  Approximately seven inches rain in past three weeks.  Last check of year- excellent clarity.
Mostly sunny- windy. Rain yesterday - .2 inches
Sunny- a very nice day with about a 10mph wind
Mostly cloudy with a 10-15 mph wind and quite cool onl in upper 60s.1/2 inch of rain recently
Mostly sunny and warm with a little breeze
Totally sunny- a nice summer day and a bit breezy. Not much rain recently. Some algae blooms in shallows
Mostly sunny with a light wind. Some algae blooms in shallows. Lake going down about 1 inch per week. No rain
Beautiful blue sky with a light wind. 1-1/4 inches of rain in past 10 days. Perfect holiday weekend!
Sunny with light wind- lake clearing up
Sunny- windy. Lake is really low
Mostly sunny and about a 10- mph wind.
Beautiful blue sky and light wind.  Some tree pollen on water.  Nice holiday weekend.
Clear sky with a light wind.  Lot of tree pollen on the water.
Sunny and a light breeze.  lots of pollen in water.
Mostly sunny and about a 10 mph wind.  Little rain in past several weeks.  Lake level down 2 inches in past 2 weeks.
Partly sunny and a little breezy.  Very little rain in past month.  Lake level keeps dropping.
Sunny- windy- 15 mph.  About an inch of rain this week.  Water level down.
Sunny- calm.  Only .03 inch of rain.  Water level dropping.
Sunny with a lite wind.  Nice day.
Partly sunny and cold with a light wind.  1 3/4 inches of rain in past week.
Sunny- warm day with light wind. Ice out about 2 weeks ago.
Sunny and a bit breezy. Some rain in the past week.
Hot and humid with a little wind. Some tree pollen on the water.
Mostly sunny with a light wnid. 2 inches of rain in the past couple of weeks. The lake actually came up a little.
Sunny and kind of windy - wind about 10 MPH. Over three inches of rain n the last 11 days.
Sunny with a light wind in sample area. Very little rain in the past two weeks.
mostly sunny with a little wind. Water is up over 12 inches from last year- but Tom and I still consider lake level low.
clear blue skies and a light wind. Better secchi depth today than 1st check of the year
light wind- just a couple of clouds - nice day. Little rain lately. Lots of boat traffic yesterday.
sunny and light wind with comfortable temperatures.
nice day today. No rain in past 3 days but in the 5 before that we've had 5.4 inches.
cloudy- light winds - temperatures in low 80's
cloudy with peaks of sun and calm to light wind. 1/2 inch of rain the other day - 1.7 inches of rain total in the past week.
nice days- in the 70's. Wind about 10 mph
partly sunny with a light wind
sunny with light wind- some tree pollen on water. first check of new year- ice out approx. 7 weeks ago
sunny with a light wind. About 1 1/2 inches of rain earlier this week
mostly sunny with a bit of haze - humidity. very little rain past several weeks
Hazy sunshine- calm wind. Ice out and heavy rain about 4 days ago.
Hazy- warm- sunny- humid. Wind at 10-15 mph. 1.5 inches of rain two days prior. A lot of rain this spring.
Mostly cloudy- breezy and cold;  about 56 degrees F with some sprinkles.
Light wind- no rain at all this week
Mostly cloudy and cool with a little wind. About 4 inches of rain in the past week.
Some sun peeking through clouds with a little wind
Partly sunny- about 10 mph wind; ice out about 5 days prior

light wind; 74F Mostly clear; calm wind in test area; about 1.6 inches of rain in past week Mostly clear; calm wind in test area; about 1.6 inches of rain in past week Mostly clear; calm wind in test area; about 1.6 inches of rain in past week Mostly clear; calm wind in test area; about 1.6 inches of rain in past week Mostly clear; calm wind in test area; about 1.6 inches of rain in past week
mostly sunny; about half inch of rain last night; very little rain in past three weeks
1 inch of rain on previous Monday; light wind; ~70F
partly sunny; light wind; rain previous morning; total of 2.5+ inches of rain over past week
warm and sunny with a light wind
Mostly clear w/ light wind- humid with a little haze.  Very little rain past 2 weeks.
Mostly sunny with a light wind
Breezy- partly sunny.  Lots of pollen on water.
Mostly sunny with a light wind. Lots of boat traffic on the weekend.
Water temp 79F- air temp 80F.  Dead calm today.
Hazy sunshine and kind of breezy
2 inches of rain last week. Water is extremely high.
3/4 inches of rain last week. Still high water.
1 inch of rain this week. Sunny and breezy.
no clouds. extremely high water level
